Package at.jku.amp.lepatriinu

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Analyzer
    Heart of detecting functionality.
    AutoCorrelationBeatDetector
    Implements three autocorrelating algorithms, which can be chosen by the setting Analyzer.AUTO_FUNCTION.
    BeatDetector
    Super class of all beat detectors.
    GroundTruthPicker
    Just a simple class that reads out the onsets of the ground truth provided.
    HighFrequencyOnsetDetector
    Uses the High Frequency Content method (slide 4.19) to extract onsets.
    InterOnsetTempoExtractor
    Uses Inter Onset Intervals (slides 5.10 - 5.14) to estimate the beat.
    OnsetDetector
    Super class of all onset detectors.
    SimpleOnsetDetector
    This is a very simple kind of Onset Detector.
    SpectralFluxOnsetDetector
    Uses the idea of Spectral Difference (slide 4.20) to extract onsets.
    TempoExtractor
    Super class of all tempo extractors.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BeatDetector.Mode
    Defines which function AutoCorrelationBeatDetector should choose when called.
